param.value: SELECT distinct cons.cons_usr_id, cons.cons_id, cons.Cons_Name, sp.sp_cd , sp.sp_name FROM ConsultM AS cons INNER JOIN ConsultLocationM AS consloc ON cons.Cons_Id = consloc.Cons_Id INNER JOIN ConsSpecialityM AS conssp ON consloc.LOC_id = conssp.Loc_ID AND consloc.Cons_Id = conssp.Cons_ID INNER JOIN SpecialityM AS sp ON cons.sp_cd = sp.Sp_Cd WHERE (cons.Cons_IsActive = 1 AND consloc.LOC_id = 1)

Select distinct A.AC_CD,AC_desc,D.Tpm_Cd,H.Tpm_name from ACCTM A Inner join CusClassLocation C on A.Ac_Cd=C.AC_CD Inner Join TestPriceMD D on C.Tpm_Cd= D.Tpm_Cd Inner Join TestPriceMH H on H.Tpm_Cd= D.Tpm_Cd where A.Is_Active=1 and A.Pymt_Mode='C' and C.LOC_id='1'
SELECT LocM.Loc_Id, LocM.Loc_Name, CoM.Co_Name FROM LocationM LocM JOIN CompM CoM ON LocM.Co_Cd = CoM.Co_Cd WHERE LocM.IsActive = 1 and LocM.Loc_Id = 1 ORDER BY LocM.Loc_Name
